:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tjGcvs8ymj03zh5mSaJBkzVBKRo=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQYFUHONJOIDBMXKUQKADHDPJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtjGcvs8ymj03zh5mSaJBkzVBKRo%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQYFUHONJOIDBMXKUQKADHDPJY.jpg&h=28d3f6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n02年6月8日清晨，康仔去台北「TeXound」酒吧狂歡，同場仲有安雅、當地DJ、藝人同模特兒。其間台警突擊搜查，發現康仔伏喺梳化，褲頭鬆脫，仲有包嘢跌落地，康仔想執但俾台警踩實，佢因涉嫌藏有搖頭丸被扣查。安雅仲離譜，驗尿時企圖用水換尿，結果當然被識穿。康仔最終被判服食二級毒品MDMA罪成，喺台灣勒戒11日後獲釋"},{"pid":"20e7cdc7520804ac68c2d948590ae8874c8cab4b","tid":2448394,"uid":245819,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5cc59b66b76860cd6811b297d27f09f9b0861f55","tid":2448394,"uid":41411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tjGcvs8ymj03zh5mSaJBkzVBKRo=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQYFUHONJOIDBMXKUQKADHDPJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtjGcvs8ymj03zh5mSaJBkzVBKRo%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQYFUHONJOIDBMXKUQKADHDPJY.jpg&h=28d3f6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n02年6月8日清晨，康仔去台北「TeXound」酒吧狂歡，同場仲有安雅、當地DJ、藝人同模特兒。其間台警突擊搜查，發現康仔伏喺梳化，褲頭鬆脫，仲有包嘢跌落地，康仔想執但俾台警踩實，佢因涉嫌藏有搖頭丸被扣查。安雅仲離譜，驗尿時企圖用水換尿，結果當然被識穿。康仔最終被判服食二級毒品MDMA罪成，喺台灣勒戒11日後獲釋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEapnRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEapnRA.gif&h=7defc123&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}